OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMurky during
OL,6,Fthe evening and overnight, with a
OL,7,Flittle rain and drizzle for a time,
OL,8,Feasing later. Areas of low cloud, mist
OL,9,Fand fog persisting in places through
OL,10,Fto dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA murky start, with cloud
OL,13,Fbreaks eventually developing to allow
OL,14,Flimited sunny intervals, with these
OL,15,Fmost likely in then east. Cloudier
OL,16,Fthroughout in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
